text: Abul Kalam Azad Siddiqui is a Bangladesh Nationalist Party politician and the former Member of Parliament of Tangail-7. ==Career== Siddiqui was elected to parliament from Tangail-7 as a Bangladesh Nationalist Party candidate in 1996. ==References== Category:Bangladesh Nationalist Party politicians Category:Living people Category:6th Jatiya Sangsad members Category:7th Jatiya Sangsad members Category:Year of birth missing (living people)
title: Abul Kalam Azad Siddiqui
